    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)"><date>Tuesday, 29th of Sivan(May), 1860</date>.</p>
            <p>Very honored Sir and friend:</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">The last “Occident” has value. The composition of
                    <persName>Gutheim</persName><lb/> is strong. <persName>Wise</persName> and his
                cronies will scratch behind their ears. I re-<lb/>ceived the copies but the last
                ones of <persName>Henry Moses</persName> are missing and I<lb/> must urgently ask
                you for the same. Above all this- the one who caused<lb/> to stop the silly stories
                of <persName>Wise</persName> shall become my agent for the stories.<lb/> What will
                you ask for the sheet if I permit them to be printed there?<lb/> Write to me about
                this just two words by return post. You may send the<lb/>
                <sic>Aoccident</sic>” to my brother-in-law <persName>Baer</persName> in
                    <placeName>Dresden</placeName>. He will pay the expres-<lb/>sage</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Don't you know of any position for me? I should like
                    <placeName>Phila-<lb/>delphia</placeName> best of all. We shall certainly work
                together and for the best.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">With hearty greetings and respect,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">Jonah of the house of Bondi</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
    </text>
